{"parse":{"title":"Felblood Snapper","pageid":93709,"wikitext":{"*":":''Did you mean the quest {{quest|Felblood Fillet}}, or the quest item {{item|Monstrous Felblood Snapper}}?''\n<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|sell={{cost|c=8}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_38\n|itemid=27441\n|flavor=A twisted fish that lives in fel pools and lava.   Do Not Eat!\n|ilvl=60\n|name=Felblood Snapper\n|quality=Poor}}</onlyinclude>\n''[[Felblood Snapper]]'' is a [[fish]] that is [[Fishing|caught]] from the green lava in [[Shadowmoon Valley]] or the [[Pools of Aggonar]] in [[Hellfire Peninsula]] - it is a gray item and has no current use other than as pet food. It was rumored to be used in a future [[Alchemy]] recipe. However since Blizzard changed the item quality from {{quality|common}} to {{quality|poor}} the rumor seems to be just a wild guess.\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|27441}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/felblood_snapper.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n[[Category:World of Warcraft fished items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft poor items]]"}}}